version_description: Newly designed user interface features Quick Balance accounts view from secure login screen. Mobile Check Deposit, Pay a Person, newly integrated Focus Money Manager application, enhanced Branch & ATM Locator, and Reset Account Password capabilities added for member convenience.

Enhancements include Multiple Memory for users with multiple accounts, account selection for Quick Balance, improved search capability for Locations and transactions, and general usability improvements.

Enhancements include a new locations search feature for the nearly 30,000 nationwide fee-free ATMs, a Pay button for simplified loan and credit card payments, integrated credit card balance, transaction, and payment information, add and manage payees and schedule recurring payments, and overall faster response times for common functions.
Touch ID is now available for a fast, secure login.

-Enroll in eStatements, manage Alerts, submit travel notices for debit and credit cards, update email address, phone, and language preference, manage person-to-person payments, register for eBills and AutoPay, view check images, and pay business loans.
-iOS11 compatibility updates
Mobile check deposit just got easier. The new auto capture feature will take the picture of your check automatically!
Updates in this release include expanded transaction history (increasing from 15 to 30 days),updated loan payoff amounts, and other smaller bug fixes.
The latest update features pay button for loan payments, Pay A Person cancel option along with several bug fixes.

-Several Bill Pay improvements
-Enhanced advance search
-Improved login process
-Other security enhancements and bug fixes
Pay a Person Mobile now offers instant payments. It's fast, secure, easy to use, and perfect for one-time payments to friends or family.

-Several Bill Pay improvements
-Enhanced advance search
-Improved login process
-Other security enhancements and bug fixes
